ARTICLE.TITLE: MPD: Woman reported missing from 35th and Wisconsin found safe
ARTICLE.TEXT:
MPD: Woman reported missing from 35th and Wisconsin found safe

Updated: 7:30 p.m. on August 12, 2020

MILWAUKEE (CBS 58) -- Milwaukee police say Latonya Kennedy has been located safely.

------

Posted: 4:37 p.m. on August 12, 2020

MILWAUKEE (CBS 58) -- Milwaukee police are investigating reports of a missing 50-year-old woman.

Authorities say Latonya R. Kennedy went missing on Saturday, Aug. 8, around 10:14 p.m., from 35th and Wisconsin.

Kennedy is described as a 50-year-old African American woman, 5'2", 375 pounds, with black hair and brown eyes.

She was last seen wearing a purple jogging suit.

Anyone with information is asked to contact MPD at 414-935-7401.
